    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Recreate a Song #2\r\n\r\nYour friend, Dylan, loves rock music. His band made this great intro riff for a new song they're working on. Use the timeline and the sounds given to you to recreate the intro to his song. \r\n\r\nDo this: \r\n\r\n- Listen to the song in the media player. \r\n- Use the sounds given to you to build the song. \r\n- Look at this timeline for reference. \r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/77e775bf2b3eb6aecb35cc41718c6d15-image-1741386018301.17.20 PM.png)",
